snippet.title: Johnny Depp Could Face Jail for Illegally Brining Dogs Into Australia
snippet.description:
The Sydney Morning Herald reports that Black Mass star, Johnny Depp, could face up to 10 years in jail for illegally bringing his two dogs, Pistol and Boo, into Australia.
